# PyMOL script to highlight allosteric sites in 3IRH
fetch 3IRH
hide everything
show cartoon, chain B
color spectrum, chain B
# Highlight allosteric residues
select resi 17 and chain B
show surface, resi 17 and chain B
color green, resi 17 and chain B
set transparency, 0.19999999999999996, resi 17 and chain B
